body.name: McKesson Baby Diaper Size 7, Over 41 lbs. BD-SZ7, 20 Ct
features: Size 7 diapers fit babies weighing 41 pounds and up, and they offer 12-hour protection for day and night wear
Snug-fit diapers have a flexible waist for comfort and a contoured design with a naval cutout to avoid irritation around the umbilical area
Integrated wetness indicator that changes color when wet to notify carers that infant needs a change of diaper to stay dry and fresh
Hook-and-loop closure for quick removal and replacement; diapers have a shaped fit at the gusset for a secure, flexible fit
Latex-free and perfume-free for delicate infant skin

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Baby Diapers Designed to keep up with children in motion, McKesson Baby Diapers feature soft, stretchable fasteners and a snug-fit waist that inhibits leaks while babies move and increases comfort. These unisex diapers are available in a variety of sizes! The diapers' superior absorbency offers up to 12 hours of protection, allowing them to be used as both daytime and overnight diapers. A built-in wetness indicator lets you know when it's time for a change. They have a soft outer cover that is not made with natural rubber latex. The baby diapers are perfume-free to minimize irritation. They have a fun graphic print. At a Glance: Disposable diapers for babiesDaytime/overnight diapers offer up to 12 hours of protectionStretchable fasteners and a snug fit waist that move with small childrenWetness indicator changes color when it's time for a change

Disposable Baby Diapers Soft and Stretchy Diapers that Move McKesson Baby Diapers are specially designed to facilitate movement without sacrificing leak protection. A shaped fit at the gusset allows the diaper to easily move with the baby, while soft, stretchable hook-and-loop fasteners ensure a secure and comfortable fit. The tabs can be easily refastened to keep the diaper fitting snugly against the body between changes. Disposable Daytime and Overnight Coverage Made with a cloth-like interior and a soft and breathable outer cover, McKesson Baby Diapers provide up to 12 hours of protection for use during the day or at night. Their mix of comfort, mobility and protection make them a versatile option for daytime play or as an overnight diaper. An integrated wetness indicator changes color when wet, alerting parents and caregivers that it’s time for a new diaper. Unisex Diapers These are unisex diapers for both little boys and girls. Each diaper features a kid-friendly colorful print design with fun graphics. The disposable diapers are designed to be soft, breathable, and free from perfumes and latex to provide a comfortable diaper solution for even the most sensitive of infants.

About McKesson For over 180 years, McKesson has supported providers with the medical supplies they need to care for patients and run a healthy business. McKesson offers more than 300,000 products from leading national brands as well as its own private product label, and a suite of services to help businesses and facilities provide quality care, improve business performance and manage time and expenses. McKesson improves the business of healthcare to help everyone focus on what matters most: patient care.
